    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or a reliable daily driver with a little work. The engine is functional and starts up, though it could benefit from a tune-up to address some minor idling inconsistencies. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, small door dings, and some fading paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and a few stains. It is a dependable car that needs some cosmetic and mechanical TLC to reach its full potential.",
