    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly an absolute dream to drive and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's in truly pristine condition inside and out. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in top-notch shape, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 44900.0,
