    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and an M-Variable Differential Lock, delivering linear power and exceptional torque vectoring. This chassis has been meticulously preserved, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural rigidity. Every bushing, seal, and the dual-VANOS system operate within factory tolerances, ensuring a visceral, purely mechanical driving experience. The factory finish is flawless, free of imperfections, and retains full depth, making this a collector-grade icon of turn-of-the-century performance engineering.",
